blackjack-pro (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major update: Professional features added
  * Multiple counting systems (Hi-Lo, KO, Omega II)
  * Deviation indices (Illustrious 18 + Fab Four)
  * Save/Load game sessions with JSON persistence
  * CSV statistics export for analysis
  * Enhanced GUI with menu system
  * Advanced analytics and advantage display

